    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The drivetrain is paired with a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term reliability, the rear subframe has been reinforced and the VANOS system has been recently overhauled. The suspension maintains its composure through corners thanks to refreshed bushings and upgraded dampers. This is a mechanically sound example with sharp throttle response and a linear power band, offering a pure analog driving experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
