    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2018 Sport Touring Sedan has been meticulously maintained and remains in impressive condition for its mileage. The exterior finish retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment with supple leather seating; the driver\u2019s bolster shows only slight softening, while the passenger and rear seats appear nearly new. All technological features, including the premium infotainment system and dual-zone climate control, function perfectly. Mechanically, this vehicle is sound, benefiting from a documented service history, including a recent full synthetic oil change and brake pad replacement. It sits on a set of high-performance tires with approximately 70% tread life remaining. This is a reliable, well-cared-for example that bridges the gap between a daily driver and a weekend enthusiast car.",
